  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463830/extras/91286ceba16158ac19cc3fd59b94098f.poster.avif?t=1773099044\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463830/extras/91286ceba16158ac19cc3fd59b94098f.webm?t=1773099044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463830/extras/91286ceba16158ac19cc3fd59b94098f.mp4?t=1773099044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a fresh graduate of the Earth Aviation Academy, you are assigned to the distant edge of known space. Investigate strange colonist behavior and deal with unknown threats in the ZPDN-A sector. <br>Hone your piloting skills, expand your arsenal, and complete your mission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463830/extras/27379b0383b70404c62dafa09881121b.avif?t=1773099044\" width=616 height=198 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Game features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 stunning levels - explore colorful alien worlds </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn points and exchange them for ammunition. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your arsenal as you go - Impulse gun, missiles, plasma gun, mines, homing shells, laser gun, energy shield, and Perun's Exhalation! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secrets lurking in space - Find and kill eight alien fish </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from three classes of spaceships to best suit your play style </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off against challenging bosses in each level </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also in the game: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escort and protect the cargo ship </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free colonists</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy!</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463830/extras/91286ceba16158ac19cc3fd59b94098f.poster.avif?t=1773099044\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463830/extras/91286ceba16158ac19cc3fd59b94098f.webm?t=1773099044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463830/extras/91286ceba16158ac19cc3fd59b94098f.mp4?t=1773099044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a fresh graduate of the Earth Aviation Academy, you are assigned to the distant edge of known space. Investigate strange colonist behavior and deal with unknown threats in the ZPDN-A sector. <br>Hone your piloting skills, expand your arsenal, and complete your mission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463830/extras/27379b0383b70404c62dafa09881121b.avif?t=1773099044\" width=616 height=198 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Game features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 stunning levels - explore colorful alien worlds </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn points and exchange them for ammunition. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your arsenal as you go - Impulse gun, missiles, plasma gun, mines, homing shells, laser gun, energy shield, and Perun's Exhalation! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secrets lurking in space - Find and kill eight alien fish </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from three classes of spaceships to best suit your play style </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off against challenging bosses in each level </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also in the game: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escort and protect the cargo ship </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free colonists</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy!</p></li></ul>",
